OL,3,CMotorcyclist dies week after west
OL,4,CBelfast road crash
OL,6,FA man has died a week after a two-
OL,7,Fvehicle collision in west Belfast.
OL,9,FTJ Kennedy, 20, from the Poleglass
OL,10,Farea, was taken to hospital for
OL,11,Fserious injuries following the
OL,12,Fcollision on July 5.
OL,14,FHe was riding a motorcycle which was
OL,15,Fin a collision with another vehicle.
OL,17,FHe died as a result of his injuries on
OL,18,FSaturday while receiving treatment in
OL,19,Fhospital.
