OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1783950571
OL,3,CMotorcyclist dies week after west
OL,4,CBelfast road crash
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "We are
OL,7,Fcontinuing to investigate the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of what happened.
OL,10,F"At approximately 6pm on Sunday, 5th
OL,11,FJuly police received a report of a
OL,12,Fcollision involving a blue Volkswagen
OL,13,FTouran and silver Yamaha Tracer in the
OL,14,FShaws Road area, at its junction with
OL,15,FGreenan.
OL,17,F"Officers along with colleagues from
OL,18,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,19,Fattended the scene ` and Mr Kennedy
OL,20,Fwas taken onward to hospital.
